sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Benutzer
    participant System as Spam-Erkennungssystem
    participant Email as E-Mail-Server

    User->>Email: Send Email
    Email->>System: Forward Email for Analysis
    System->>System: Analyze Email Content
    System->>System: Check Spam Criteria
    alt Spam Detected
        System->>Email: Mark as Spam
        Email->>User: Notify User (Spam Detected)
    else Not Spam
        System->>Email: Deliver Email
        Email->>User: Notify User (Email Delivered)
    end